Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)}{\fs20\pos(375,220)}Alioth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)}{\pos(289,361)}開陽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)}{\fs20\pos(289,328)}Mizar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)}{\pos(600,458)}搖光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,300)}{\fs20\pos(600,425)}Alkaid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那個曲線延伸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是橙色的「麥星」  牧夫座的大角星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(460,435)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(556,369)}大角星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\fs20\pos(556,336)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲線再延伸的話就是室女座的角宿一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(453,435)}Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(520,380)}角宿一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fad(500,300)\pos(520,347)}Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是淡淡的白色的「珍珠星」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}{\fs18\pos(358,242)}春天大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}{\fs18\pos(269,216)}春天大鑽石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(403,80)}五帝座一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\fs20\pos(403,47)}Denebola
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些全部連起來的話就是春天大曲線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大三角或者鑽石的也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是最喜歡這條曲線了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像搖椅一樣讓人想橫躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這個因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得比起靠看書來想象尺寸大很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為星座是比較整齊地結合起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也試著看看死兆星？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者看看星雲什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我要看我要看我要看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部的小部件set on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我可以摸摸看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:05.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小夜學姐  不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…晚上像這樣會突然覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時總是在那樣的亮光裡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想夜晚對誰來說都是一樣地到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過的方式卻有很多種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是不是在說些很理所當然的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有回到這小鎮來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天我可能在某個市鎮裡讀著書了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀著書是不會想到在屋頂上閃耀中的小小光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜寂  黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道很多的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我所認識的夜晚幾乎都在日光燈下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微放心點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想著你會不會還在意小學時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…都已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話…就有一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼呢  快點來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木  怎麼辦  我覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說M78星雲的M  可不是奧特曼的用語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:43.07,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\alpha&H50&\fs20}注：M78星雲  是在奧特曼裡登場的一個虛構星雲  是奧特曼的故鄉  設定距離銀河系為300萬光年  別名為光之國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川同學  優秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒了  我燃燒起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光  市鎮的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們本身並沒有好壞之分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的夜晚  也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我就不想了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能輸
